<DIV2 TYPE="hymn">
<HEAD>Children devoted to GOD.
<HI>Gen.</HI> 17.7, 10. <HI>Acts</HI> 16.14, 15, 33.</HEAD>
<LG N="1">
<HEAD>1</HEAD>
<L>THus &s;aith the Mercy of the Lord,</L>
<L><HI>I'll be a God to thee;</HI></L>
<L><HI>I'll ble&s;s thy num'rous Race, and they</HI></L>
<L><HI>Shall be a Seed for me.</HI></L>
</LG>
<LG N="2">
<HEAD>2</HEAD>
<L><HI>Abraham</HI> believ'd the promis'd Grace,</L>
<L>And gave his Sons to God;</L>
<L>But Water &s;eals the Ble&s;&s;ing now,</L>
<L>That once was &s;eal'd with Blood.</L>
</LG>
<LG N="3">
<HEAD>3</HEAD>
<L>Thus <HI>Lydia</HI> &s;anctify'd her Hou&s;e</L>
<L>When &s;he receiv'd the Word;</L>
<L>Thus the believing Jaylor gave</L>
<L>His Hou&s;hold to the Lord,</L>
</LG>
<LG N="4">
